  <brief_title>Long-Term Safety of Symbicort in Asthmatic Children - SAPLING</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Six Month, Randomized, Open-Label, Safety Study of Symbicort (160/4.5mcg) Compared to Pulmicort Turbuhaler in Asthmatic Children Aged Six to Eleven Years - SAPLING</official_title>
